GD-Graph-Thermometer version 0.0.1

This module may be used to create a thermometer graphic which
can track progress on a fundraising or other campaign, to
graphically represent progress to a pre-defined goal.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires GD and GD::Text::Align in order to work.

